## Linting & formatting
- ESLint: Flat config `eslint.config.js` with Next, TypeScript, React Hooks.
- Scope: Lint `src/**`; ignore build outputs and tool configs.
- Prettier 3: default formatting, no project-level overrides.
- ESLint is blocking; fix warnings and errors before commit/PR.
